# Leave unset so the browser calls same-origin `/api/...` and Vite proxies (recommended for dev).
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=

# Where Vite forwards `/api` (read by vite.config.ts via loadEnv + process.env).
# - Local UI + API on host: default is http://127.0.0.1:8000 (start uvicorn there).
# - Docker Compose already sets http://backend:8000 on the frontend container.
# VITE_DEV_PROXY_TARGET=http://127.0.0.1:8000
